                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/81224130-3caa-46cf-92ae-df60196f3aa6&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/81224130-3caa-46cf-92ae-df60196f3aa6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_27ab failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
