&lt;pre&gt;usr/bin/lfs setquota -u quota_usr -b 53856644 -B 56549476 -i 838864 -I 880807 /mnt/lustre
lfs setquota: quotactl failed: Operation not permitted
setquota failed: Operation not permitted
