&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4609&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4609&lt;/a&gt; - 5.15.0-88-generic&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4609&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4609&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-427.42.1_lustre.el9.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;this has suddenly started failing across all branches so I suspect it is one of the recent patch landings, which were quickly backported to b_es6_0/b_es7_0.&lt;/p&gt;







